subject: IDEA: add thread functionality to boards; archive command
message:
It would be cool if it were possible for players to reply to posts on boards,
and we could show the whole message thread together.

Another idea: add a 'board move <src> <dest>' to move posts from one board
from one board to another.  Maybe allow referencing specific post numbers
so we wouldn't have to move all the messages at once.  Something like
    board move mortal:1-25 archive
    board move mortal:26 spam
    board move quest qhistory

Also, it would be nice if the /f and /fi commands were paragraph-aware.
